00:27:36.350 --> 00:27:38.890
portfolio plays a
role going forward,

00:27:38.890 --> 00:27:42.200
specifically Ted and
Todd's role going forward?

00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:43.490
How important will it be?

00:27:43.490 --> 00:27:44.480
LARRY CUNNINGHAM: OK.

00:27:44.480 --> 00:27:45.646
Shall I take that one first?

00:27:45.646 --> 00:27:46.490
That's great.

00:27:46.490 --> 00:27:50.270
I think it's true that in
terms of Berkshire overall,

00:27:50.270 --> 00:27:53.230
